,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"香港人從來最怕事最功利最自私<br />\n但係呢兩年train到大家可以走出黎<br />\n<br />\n大家，風高浪急，好好企穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9070bb8ea2b3d5b739d2e386c8a655dd0333c4e","tid":2155630,"uid":29938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:02:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2624f18c3d1b0cb8b4625beb13df8a25e34d8fcd","tid":2155630,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}